Genre type: RPG

**Player stats:** 
starting health - 100 

**Class**
Warrior: Strength: +15; Mana: +10
Mage: Strength: +5; Mana: +20

Starting Point: Village 

Player meets instructor & choose his/her class; if you choose warrior class, show stat, are you sure: yes/ no / returns 

Go to Dungeon: 

Fight a monster - 100 healths points 

player attacks, damages 15 health points 

monster attack, damages 10 

return to village, and buy potions from instructor 

potions will restore 30 health